The <title> of the nim-lang.org homeage is "Nim Programming Language" and is consistent with COMMENT standards of not using a leading indefinite article. 

In this case the modified COMMENT is valid (and is substantiated by upstream language).

@Torsten, please use See Also for issues that refer to this or are related to other issues. Depends/Blocks is exactly and only for when listed issues MUST be resolved prior to, or after this one, respectively.
